window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Hey. You looking for a steamy single parent romantic comedy? How about three single dad steamy rom coms and one single mom steamy rom com?</p> <p>The Name in Lights Collection contains three full standalone novels and a bonus novelette that's set in the same world. What's a novelette, you might ask? It's slightly shorter than a novella and longer than a short story, but equally as entertaining as a novel. Really!<br> <br> <b>SLEEPER:</b> <i>a single dad - nanny / brother's best friend romance</i><br> Shane and Willa's story.<br> This collection contains a bonus epilogue that is not included in the original publication.<br> <br> <b>CHARMER: </b><i>a single mom - rockstar romance</i><br> Nico and Kat's story.<br> <br> <b>TROUBLEMAKER:</b> <i>a single dad - teacher romance</i><br> Alex and Emilia's story.<br> Get to know The Lazy Wingmen.<br> <br> <b>PUMPKIN'S GOTTA GIVE:</b> <i>a single dad - neighbor romance</i><br> Damon and Nikki's story.<br> Set during Thanksgiving--there's much ado about stuffing and there's a wiener dog named Dildo. You're welcome, world.</p>"; 
